WEBVTT

00:00:00.003 --> 00:00:03.000
- From smartphones to streaming music

00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:06.004
technology has changed the way we live our everyday lives.

00:00:06.004 --> 00:00:10.004
As technology impacts more of how we do what we do,

00:00:10.004 --> 00:00:12.003
you don't want to be left behind

00:00:12.003 --> 00:00:15.002
with a rotary phone and eight track player.

00:00:15.002 --> 00:00:18.000
Learning new technical skills can help you reach more

00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:20.002
of your personal and professional goals.

00:00:20.002 --> 00:00:22.009
From using spreadsheets to easily keeping track

00:00:22.009 --> 00:00:25.005
of your monthly budget, to updating your resume

00:00:25.005 --> 00:00:27.003
to make it really stand out.

00:00:27.003 --> 00:00:30.007
I'm Courtney Hodge, a program manager at Microsoft

00:00:30.007 --> 00:00:32.007
and I'm passionate about helping people

00:00:32.007 --> 00:00:35.007
use technology to make their lives easier.

00:00:35.007 --> 00:00:40.002
In this course, I'll teach you the basics of Microsoft 365.

00:00:40.002 --> 00:00:42.007
So you can start using these powerful tools

00:00:42.007 --> 00:00:44.008
to make your life easier.

00:00:44.008 --> 00:00:46.002
I'll share the ins and outs

00:00:46.002 --> 00:00:49.002
of document creation with Microsoft Word.

00:00:49.002 --> 00:00:52.006
I'll show you how to create tables and charts with Excel.

00:00:52.006 --> 00:00:54.002
I'll walk you through easy

00:00:54.002 --> 00:00:57.003
and accessible ways of implementing OneNote.

00:00:57.003 --> 00:01:00.007
I'll also help you connect and communicate more effectively.

00:01:00.007 --> 00:01:02.005
in Outlook and PowerPoint.

00:01:02.005 --> 00:01:05.004
This course is all about helping you learn

00:01:05.004 --> 00:01:07.007
how to use the latest technology

00:01:07.007 --> 00:01:10.001
to start reaching your goals.

00:01:10.001 --> 00:01:11.007
Are you with me?

00:01:11.007 --> 00:01:12.009
Let's get started.